            7
          ],
          1,
          "bigger checks"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". The entire situation shows that Joe Biden and Democratic congressional leaders either could have driven a much tougher bargain in their negotiations over new COVID-19 relief legislation with Republican Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell — or they actually "
