        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            13
          ],
          1,
          "pretending"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " she’s always been ready to take Trump up on his offer to support $2,000 survival checks, even though prior to about an hour ago, she had never tried to triangulate Trump against McConnell on the issue. Earlier this month, she supported a deal that "
